headline: Mizuho Maintains Outperform on Willis Towers Watson, Lowers Price Target to $358
summary: Mizuho  analyst Yaron Kinar   maintains Willis Towers Watson (NASDAQ:WTW) with a Outperform and lowers the price target from $392 to $358.
